# fitting

## Stack
- Expo Router + Supabase + TypeScript

## Supabase client
- Use the root-level `supabase.ts` export for the Supabase client (do not duplicate client setup elsewhere unless there is a clear reason).

## Auth
- Use `supabase.auth` for authentication.

## Routing
- `app/(auth)/` — login and signup flows
- `app/(tabs)/` — main app (tab navigation)

## Database
- User profile data: `public.users` table in Supabase

## Done (baseline)
- Login
- Signup step 1

## Styling
- Use React Native `StyleSheet` for styles (not Tailwind/CSS-in-JS alternatives unless already introduced).

## Repository
- https://github.com/fitting0607-blip/fitting.git
